WEBVTT

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:30.640
inspire the flow of life-giving waters.

00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:34.736
As you can see then,

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:38.176
Khmer classical dance
is a transformation of nature,

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:42.320
of both the physical world around us
and of our own internal universe.

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:46.256
We have four primary
hand gestures that we use.

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:47.480
Can we do them together?

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:50.000
Yeah? OK.

00:01:52.080 --> 00:01:53.960
This is a tree.

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:57.200
That tree will grow,

00:01:58.480 --> 00:02:01.520
and then it will have leaves.